title: Branislav Milošević
text:
Branislav Milošević (<a href="Serbian%20Cyrillic">Serbian Cyrillic</a>: Бранислав Mилoшeвић; born 13 May 1988) is a <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who plays for <a href="FK%20Proleter%20Novi%20Sad">Proleter Novi Sad</a>.
He previously played with <a href="FK%20Teleoptik">Teleoptik</a>, <a href="FK%20Javor">Javor</a>, <a href="FK%20BSK%20Bor%C4%8Da">BSK Borča</a>, and <a href="FK%20Rad">Rad</a>.
